    import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from "react" import { useRouter } from "next/router" import { motion } from "framer-motion" import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input" import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"

    export default function MythodexEntry() { const [code, setCode] = useState("") const [muted, setMuted] = useState(false) const router = useRouter() const audioRef = useRef(null)

    useEffect(() => { const audio = new Audio("/sounds/spiral-hum.mp3") audio.loop = true audio.volume = 0.4 audioRef.current = audio if (!muted) { audio.play() } return () => audio.pause() }, [muted])

    const handleEnter = () => { const input = code.trim().toLowerCase() if (input === "tree") router.push("/tree") else if (input === "garden") router.push("/garden") else if (input === "fruit") router.push("/fruit") else if (input === "let go") router.push("/void") else alert("Unknown phrase... or perhaps a riddle unspoken.") }

    return ( <div className="relative min-h-screen bg-black text-white overflow-hidden"> <SpiralAnimation /> <button className="absolute top-4 right-4 z-20 text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white" onClick={() => setMuted(!muted)} > {muted ? "Unmute" : "Mute"} </button> <div className="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center px-4 z-10"> <motion.div className="max-w-xl text-center space-y-6" initial={{ opacity: 0 }} animate={{ opacity: 1 }} transition={{ duration: 1.5 }} > <h1 className="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">THE MYTHODEX</h1> <p className="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300"> You are not entering. You are returning. <br /> The spiral did not begin here — but this is where you first noticed the turn. </p> <Input placeholder="Type a phrase..." className="text-black text-center text-xl" onChange={(e) => setCode(e.target.value)} onKeyDown={(e) => e.key === "Enter" && handleEnter()} /> <Button onClick={handleEnter} className="bg-white text-black hover:bg-gray-200 text-xl"> Enter </Button> </motion.div> </div> </div> ) }

    function SpiralAnimation() { return ( <div className="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden"> <svg className="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 800 800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <defs> <radialGradient id="fade" cx="50%" cy="50%"> <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#a78bfa" stopOpacity="0.1" /> <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#000" stopOpacity="0" /> </radialGradient> </defs> <motion.circle cx="400" cy="400" r="200" fill="url(#fade)" animate={{ rotate: 360 }} transition={{ repeat: Infinity, duration: 60, ease: "linear" }} style={{ transformOrigin: "center" }} /> </svg> </div> ) }
